entries.femaleVariant:
David: Barghest had the whole of Dogtown locked down for the night while they searched for her.
Iron: I can't believe Hanson shot down Space Force One, the guy must have lost it!
David: He's claiming it crashed but I saw the smoke trail from here boss, clear as day.
Iron: The NUSA won't take this lying down. FIA agents are probably infiltrating the Saphire already.
David: Everyone's on edge from Luxor Heights to the Stacks, jumping at shadows.
Iron: Fine steel in your hand will help calm those fears - that's your pitch today.
David: I've had several customers already this morning.
Iron: A little chaos is good for business. I should give Hands a call...

Are you down on your luck or on the run?
Have you fallen off Skid Row and ended up in Dogtown?
Did you pawn your Katana for Black Lace?
And your favourite Tomahawk got stuck in a Scav skull this morning?

Then come on down to the Sky Gym in Longshore Stacks where our staff will help you find the melee weapon of your dreams!
